title: 1964–65 Yugoslav Cup
text:
The 1964–65 <a href="Yugoslav%20Cup">Yugoslav Cup</a> was the 18th season of the top <a href="association%20football">football</a> knockout competition in <a href="SFR%20Yugoslavia">SFR Yugoslavia</a>, the Yugoslav Cup (), also known as the "<a href="Josip%20Broz%20Tito">Marshal Tito</a> Cup" ("Kup Maršala Tita"), since its establishment in 1946.
Round of 16.
In the following tables winning teams are marked in bold; teams from outside top level are marked in "italic" script.
